P(D|A) = 0.005 = 5/1000 = 1/200
P(D|B) = 0.008 = 8/1000 = 4/500 = 2/ 250 = 1/125
P(D|C) = 0.010 = 10/1000 = 1/100

P(A)   = 1/7
P(B)   = 2/7
P(C)   = 4/7

P(D) = P(A)*P(D|A)+P(B)*P(D|B)+P(C)*P(D|C)=1/7*1/200+2/7*1/125+4/7*1/100 = (5+8*2+10*4)/(7*1000)=61/(7*1000)

P(A|D)= [P(D|A)*P(A)]/P(D)=(5/7*1000)*(7*1000/61)=5/61

